tweets.text: With #Barry expected to poise a serious inland flood hazard this weekend, here are some tips on what to do now before the storm arrives.  For more on Barry, see https://t.co/tW4KeGdBFb or https://t.co/SiZo8ozBbn https://t.co/ehXQZ5H7eA
